channel.title: Server list ISSUE!
channel.description:
So,
I don't really know why, but it just won't put my server on the list... I've already registered 1 server like 2 months ago and I did everything right.. But now, for the 3rd time.. It just won't work....
I register the account, I stay logged on it for about 5 minutes. Than I log off. After 24 hours waiting nothing... I did it 3 times now.. Same problem.
Can anyone help please?
